This folder is an app inside a monorepo. All packages inside the monorepo use NPM workspaces. Actually, prefer to use `pnpm` instead of `npm`, because pnpm works better with monorepo workspaces.

Path to this app is `./apps/data`. Path from this app to the monorepo root is `../../`.

It is a NextJS version 14 app which focuses on managing user accounts, visualizing and managing data from the database. It manages all data for all apps, not only related to user accounts, but logs, orders, trades, and other stuff saved to the database.

This app is a central hub of common reusable functionality imported by all other apps in the monorepo. Some are simple utility functions, while others are server actions (API endpoints generated by NextJS framework to perform secure logic in the server and returning data to the browser in the app that made the request).
